  {
   "id": "text-9581",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1205,
   "y": 2574,
   "width": 341.32,
   "height": 315.0,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 297011,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 929357,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "④ T1 pre-triage agents  [design]\n   gather context → operational RCA draft\n   + confidence + proposed actions\n   (donors: ai-incident-agent nodes,\n    PB-SRE specialists: gpu-health, scaling…)\n④ T2 advisory — remediation proposals\n\n⑤ Harness core  [merged, tested]\n   tiers T1–T4 + degrade-on-low-confidence\n   action-tier table (SR 11-7)\n   verdicts PROCEED/BLOCK/REQUIRE_HUMAN\n\n⑥ Executors\n   T4: restart stateless · re-sync · scale —\n   bounded, reversible, monitored, haltable\n   T3: executes only after on-call approve\n\n⑦ Learning: postmortem draft, runbook→skill PR",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "④ T1 pre-triage agents  [design]\n   gather context → operational RCA draft\n   + confidence + proposed actions\n   (donors: ai-incident-agent nodes,\n    PB-SRE specialists: gpu-health, scaling…)\n④ T2 advisory — remediation proposals\n\n⑤ Harness core  [merged, tested]\n   tiers T1–T4 + degrade-on-low-confidence\n   action-tier table (SR 11-7)\n   verdicts PROCEED/BLOCK/REQUIRE_HUMAN\n\n⑥ Executors\n   T4: restart stateless · re-sync · scale —\n   bounded, reversible, monitored, haltable\n   T3: executes only after on-call approve\n\n⑦ Learning: postmortem draft, runbook→skill PR",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
