   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "PUSH (accepts):\n• operator watch events\n• webhooks (CI, GitHub,\n  alert streams)\n\nPULL (connectors ~16):\n• git, fs, Jira, Slack,\n  Datadog, PagerDuty,\n  AWS, S3, OTel…\n\nNATS JetStream → parse\n→ chunk → embed → index\n+ DLQ, dedup  [live]",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "PUSH (accepts):\n• operator watch events\n• webhooks (CI, GitHub,\n  alert streams)\n\nPULL (connectors ~16):\n• git, fs, Jira, Slack,\n  Datadog, PagerDuty,\n  AWS, S3, OTel…\n\nNATS JetStream → parse\n→ chunk → embed → index\n+ DLQ, dedup  [live]",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
