   "text": "• OutcomeEvent stream\n  (ADR-0003 I6): class, tier,\n  verdict, gate, landed_at\n• Autonomous Yield · escape\n  rate · MTTR · T4-share\n• escape join: returns ↔\n  task_id (I8)  [design]",
